amily: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">激励企业提高自身信用管理</span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">提高贸易供应链货物安全系数</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">AEO<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（</span>AuthorizedEconomicOperator<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">）</span>,<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">即“经认证的经营者”。海关对信用状况、守法程度和安全措施较好的企业进行认证，对通过认证的企业提供通关便利和优惠政策。</span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">从</span>2014<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年起，海关根据企业信用状况将企业认定为认证企业、一般信用企业和失信企业。其中认证企业包括高级认证企业和一般认证企业。按照诚信守法便利、失信违法惩戒原则，分别适用相应的管理措施。（海关总署令</span>225<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">号第三条）</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">通过海关</span>AEO<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">认证的企业，不仅在中国海关、国内相关部门享受便利，还可以享受在</span>AEO<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">互认的国家和地区给予的优惠措施。目前</span>AEO<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">已被公认为全球贸易的绿色通行证。</span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-bottom: 2px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; opacity: 0.4; background-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 6px; max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; opacity: 0.6; background-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 6px; max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; opacity: 0.8; background-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 6px; max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><section style=\"margin-left: 2px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; font-size: 20.8px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">伍</span></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">货物简要描述要求完整准确</span>&nbsp;<br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">海关对货物申报内容实施负面清单管理</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">海关总署公告</span>2014<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年第</span>70<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">号中规定，舱单商品项简要描述应填写货物的商品品名，及足以鉴别货物的性质的简明描述。在实际舱单的传输过程中，“货物简要描述”经常出现过于笼统，难以辨认的情况。</span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">此次调整明确指出海关对货物简要描述实施负面清单管理，进一步要求货物申报完整准确。从负面清单中可以看出，可接受的货物简要描述应该具体、清晰，一般包含货物的材质、名称、用途、状态等内容。</span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">例如铁管包含了表示材质的铁和用途的管，相应的铁或者铁制品等笼统的货物简要描述则不被接受。这项调整有利于加强海关监管的针对性。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p></div>', null, '2017-12-27 14:49:47', '2018-01-05 09:14:51');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('18', '“治超”新政频出，企业应如何降低物流成本', '带你了解新政策！！！！', '2', '0', '0', '2', '1', '4', '4', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_课程封面5-5a4371f353b28.png', '0.01', '这两个政策给整个物流行业带来了巨大影响--什么是VGM？--为什么要实施VGM?--VGM实施内容是什么？', '1', '<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">去年，物流行业发布了两个重磅消息：</span></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88603\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 1em auto; max-width: 100%; border: none; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; border-left: 2px solid rgb(228, 74, 64); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding: 0.2em 0em; max-width: 100%; overflow: hidden; text-align: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding: 0.8em; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(232, 232, 231); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; font-size: 0.875em; line-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.交通运输部印发《整治公路货车违法超限超载行为专项行动方案》的通知。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.国际海事组织（IMO）发布了将实施《国际海上人命安全公约》（SOLAS公约）关于出口集装箱重量查核（VGM）的相关要求的消息。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这两个政策给整个物流行业带来了巨大影响，都在传达一个信号，就是：<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">严治超载</strong></span>！</span></p>', '<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">长期以来，物流成本一直占据着企业生产成本的40%以上，企业也是想尽办法降低物流成本，但绝大部分企业都是简单地通过“超载”的方式来实现，实际效果不佳，也承担着巨大处罚风险。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">现在，让我们了解IMO发布的VGM政策。</span></p><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></h1><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"41173\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgb(170, 166, 149); border-top-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-right-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-left-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-original-title=\"\" placeholder=\"1\" title=\"\" aria-describedby=\"tooltip806827\" style=\"margin-right: 8px; padding: 4px 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; float: left; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1</span><strong class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">什么是VGM？</strong></p></section><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">国际海事组织（IMO）发布了将实施《国际海上人命安全公约》（SOLAS）关于出口集装箱重量查核（VGM）的相关要求的消息，规定要求自2016年7月1 日起，提单上的托运人向海运承运人或码头代表提供集装箱重量，否则集装箱不再允许装载。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">各位货主们请注意抓重点，“<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如托运人不如实进行VGM申报的话，承运人有权拒绝承运</span>”。也就意味：<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">船东拒载</span>！相信各位货主也明白船期延误带来的后果是什么，就是：交期延误，意味着货主将面临巨大的索赔风险。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"41173\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgb(170, 166, 149); border-top-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-right-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-left-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-original-title=\"\" placeholder=\"1\" title=\"\" style=\"margin-right: 8px; padding: 4px 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; float: left; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2</span><strong class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">为什么要实施VGM?</strong></p></section><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">国际海事组织（IMO）为了提升海上安全和确保货品、集装箱以及整个集装箱运输过程中所涉及各个方面减低危险系数起到重要的作用。可以总结为以下两点：</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"85398\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 2px solid rgb(117, 117, 118); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -8px; margin-right: 18.1875px; margin-left: 18.1875px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; height: 8px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" data-style=\"text-align:justify\" style=\"margin: 15px 10px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.增加海上运输安全，保证船只船员航行安全。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.减少因虚报集装箱重量造成不合理配载而导致的航运事故。</span></p></section><section style=\"margin-right: 18.1875px; margin-bottom: -4px; margin-left: 18.1875px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（“多装多运”船只海难现场图）</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在VGM措施实施以前，托运人为节省海运成本，采取“多装多运”，货物装柜重量超过了集装箱最大限重，长期存在集装箱重量虚报、瞒报的现象，船东和码头无法准确地根据集装箱的实际重量而配载，因此产生如码头设备损坏、集装箱掉落等重大安全事故比比皆是。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">船东在集装箱装船的时候是按照订舱给的数据去分配，要保证航行过程中船身的平衡。由于订舱数据误差太大，导致不平衡配船的情况经常发生，并且有多次侧翻和船体破裂的事故发生，严重危害了海上人员安全。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"41173\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgb(170, 166, 149); border-top-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-right-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-left-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-original-title=\"\" placeholder=\"1\" title=\"\" style=\"margin-right: 8px; padding: 4px 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; float: left; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3</span><strong class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">VGM实施内容是什么？</strong></p></section><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">新规定明确表示：</span></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86517\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; max-width: 100%; border-top: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: -1px; padding-top: 6px; padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-top: 2px solid rgb(239, 112, 96); display: inline-block; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.托运人需要负责提供集装箱重量</span></strong></p></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">托运人指得是提单上的发货人（shipper），可以是货主，也可以是第三方代理公司。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86517\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; max-width: 100%; border-top: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: -1px; padding-top: 6px; padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-top: 2px solid rgb(239, 112, 96); display: inline-block; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.称重方式：</span></strong></p></section></section><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"85988\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border: none; display: inline-block; width: 469px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -2px; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: bold; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.7; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.5; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.3; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span></span></section><section style=\"margin-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（1）整体称重法，也就是整体过磅。</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">货物装箱完毕，柜门关闭并施封后，托运人可自行或者委托第三方(比如港口码头或地磅计量单位)使用经过计量监督部门认证的设备对集装箱进行整体称重。在港口有吊柜设备的情况，可直接对集装箱进行整体称重，得到的重量就是VGM申报的最终重量。在无吊柜设备的情况，装载有集装箱的拖车整体过磅, 取得的总重量减去拖车头,车架以及油箱的重量,得出的结果就是所需的VGM重量。</span></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"85988\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border: none; display: inline-block; width: 469px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -2px; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: bold; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.7; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.5; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.3; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span></span></section><section style=\"margin-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（2）重量累加法</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">即对货物毛重、包装材料重量、集装箱皮重相加，得出最终的VGM重量。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">此方法相比整体称重法会更繁琐，并且在计算过程中容易出现差错，导致申报的重量与实际重量不符，产生船公司拒载或海事罚款等严重后果。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"41173\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !i