&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">马士基航运(MAERSK)</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 12px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">达飞航运（CMA-CGM）</span></p><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"41173\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgb(170, 166, 149); border-top-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-right-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-left-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-original-title=\"\" placeholder=\"1\" title=\"\" style=\"margin-right: 8px; padding: 4px 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; float: left; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">5</span><strong class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">瞒报、虚报面临的后果</strong></p></section><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86152\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span data-bgopacity=\"40%\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 0.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgba(89, 155, 171, 0.6); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span data-bgopacity=\"25%\" style=\"margin-top: 2px; margin-bottom: 2px; max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 0.6; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgba(89, 155, 171, 0.75); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 1; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(89, 155, 171); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></span></section><section style=\"padding-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 19.2px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.&nbsp; 货物不能装船。</span></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在中国，交通运输部发布的关于执行《SOLAS公约》修订版的通知（征求意见稿）要求，承运载货集装箱的码头经营人，应当在载货集装箱装船前获得托运人提供的载货集装箱重量验证信息；对于未取得重量验证信息的载货集装箱，码头经营人不得安排该载货集装箱装船。简而言之，就是<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">船东拒载，货物滞留港口，货物未能及时装船，将会产生大量的异常费用；</span>此外，货物的交期也将会受到影响，也会面临收货人的索赔。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86152\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span data-bgopacity=\"40%\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 0.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgba(89, 155, 171, 0.6); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span data-bgopacity=\"25%\" style=\"margin-top: 2px; margin-bottom: 2px; max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 0.6; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgba(89, 155, 171, 0.75); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 0.6em; height: 0.6em; display: block; opacity: 1; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(89, 155, 171); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></section><section style=\"padding-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 19.2px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.&nbsp; 各国海事部门的处罚。</span></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">各国海事主管部门将对集装箱重量进行抽查，如发现集装箱实际重量与VGM申报重量不符，将会对船公司进行处罚，发货人有责任承担因VGM信息缺失而在全球港口可能产生的费用和处罚。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 0em; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">从2016年7月1日VGM正式实施后，绝大部分托运人都能按规定如实进行VGM申报，但也有一小部分托运人无如实进行申报。VGM申报是全球内实施的一项政策，为了避免你的货物因VGM申报不过关而导致货物交期延误产生损失，希望各位货主及代理公司都能严格高效的执行相关政策，共同塑造一个更安全的海上运输环境。</span></p><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"41173\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgb(170, 166, 149); border-top-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-right-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); border-left-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-original-title=\"\" placeholder=\"1\" title=\"\" style=\"margin-right: 8px; padding: 4px 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; float: left; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">6</span><strong class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(170, 166, 149); color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">企业应如何降低物流成本？</strong></p></section><h1 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6em; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></h1><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">企业想通过“超载“来降低物流成本已经变得不可行，而且承担了更大的处罚风险。那企业还能通过什么方式来降低物流成本呢？我们可通过下列方式来：</span></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86456\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; height: 16px; width: 1.5em; float: left; border-top: 0.15em solid rgb(198, 198, 199); border-right-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); border-bottom-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); border-left: 0.15em solid rgb(198, 198, 199); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; height: 16px; width: 1.5em; float: right; border-top: 0.15em solid rgb(198, 198, 199); border-right: 0.15em solid rgb(198, 198, 199); border-bottom-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); border-left-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><section data-bgless=\"lighten\" data-bglessp=\"15%\" style=\"margin: -0.9em 0.1em; padding: 0.8em; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(131, 87, 87); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 248); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4; word-break: break-all;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.&nbsp; 科学制定生产计划表，提前规划物流方案</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.&nbsp; 科学管理物流供应商，选取最优报价方案</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3.&nbsp; 加强物流部门人员培训，提高物流专业知识，降低报关差错风险</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.&nbsp; 建立物流风险监管与控制制度，预防物流异常费用产生</span></p></section></section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; height: 16px; width: 1.5em; float: left; border-bottom: 0.15em solid rgb(198, 198, 199); border-top-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); border-right-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); border-left: 0.15em solid rgb(198, 198, 199); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; height: 16px; width: 1.5em; float: right; border-bottom: 0.15em solid rgb(198, 198, 199); border-top-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); border-right: 0.15em solid rgb(198, 198, 199); border-left-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section></section></section><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"16401\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">降低物流成本是需要建立一套科学的物流管理制度，而并不是简单地通过“超载”实现，随着“治超”力度的不断加大，企业面临的处罚风险也日益剧增，希望企业都能自觉遵守相关的法律法规。</span></span></p>', null, '2017-12-27 18:17:23', '2017-12-28 10:48:15');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('19', '进出口货物被行政处罚怎么破？', '怎么办怎么办怎么办', '3', '0', '0', null, '2', '3', '0', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_22-5a4380206379d.png', '0.00', '为什么越努力，越焦虑？--怎么防止一步步走向平庸--怎么处理「办公室那点事儿」？--怎么和上级下级沟通--性格不强势的人怎么更好地发展--怎么解决「跳槽也搞不定」的问题', '0', '<ul style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-position: inside; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">1.怎样适应陌生的工作环境？</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">2.怎么面对批评？</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">3.怎么控制我们的工作情绪？</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">4.为什么越努力越焦虑？</li></ul>', '<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在2017年10月11日，海关总署发布了2017第48号公告，自2018年1月1日始，除特殊的几种业务类型外，取消转关申报模式。（</span><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">详情请点击</strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">：</span><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMTE3MjgyNQ==&amp;mid=2650607434&amp;idx=3&amp;sn=d3128aa22bf04adb100bae5e73978f86&amp;chksm=8ef85d7cb98fd46a65ca8c17354f38ef1d4440e8a0dcf84657de1c96430707c47ea21fdc2814&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 127, 166); max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">重磅！海关总署规范转关运输业务，明年1月1日起施行</a><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">）企业只能采用通关一体化方式或直接到进出境口岸清关。</span></p><h2 style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: auto; line-height: 1.6em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></h2><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">看到这个通知，相信大家对此产生了许多困惑</span></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"85502\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 2.5em 10px 1em 2em; max-width: 100%; border: 0px rgb(157, 180, 194); line-height: 25px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.4; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: -55px; margin-left: -30px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; float: left; transform: rotate(-5deg); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 32px; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 117) 0px 1px 8px; border-color: rgb(157, 180, 194); background-color: rgb(157, 180, 194); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 20px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">科普</span></section><section style=\"margin-left: -1px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border-left: 15px solid rgb(157, 180, 194); color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-top: 15px solid transparent !important; border-bottom: 18px solid transparent !important;\"></section></section></section><section class=\"\" data-style=\"line-height:24px;color:rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size:14px\" style=\"padding: 20px 20px 18px 50px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; box-shadow: rgb(117, 117, 117) 0px 0px 5px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 24px; text-align: center; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">全国通关一体化</span></strong></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">A：什么是全国通关一体化？</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所谓通关一体化改革，是指企业可以任意选择通关或者报关地点和口岸，在全国任何一个地方都可办理相关手续。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">B：通关一体化对企业有什么好处？</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（1）可以选择任意地点进行报关，消除了申报的关区限制；</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（2）海关执法更统一，在两个中心的处置下，全国通关的政策和规定在执行标准上更加一致；<br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（3）效率大大提高，简化了口岸通关环节的手续，压缩了口岸通关的时间。</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">首先，我们来看看原公告，有哪几种特殊业务类型还能继续选择转关申报？</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88603\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 1em auto; max-width: 100%; border: none; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; border-left: 2px solid rgb(228, 74, 64); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding: 0.2em 0em; max-width: 100%; overflow: hidden; text-align: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding: 0.8em; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(232, 232, 231); text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 0.875em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、多式联运货物，以及具有全程提（运）单需要在境内换装运输工具的；</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、进口固体废物且满足相关条件的；</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、易受温度、静电、粉尘等自然因素影响或者因他特殊原因，不宜在口岸海关监管区实施查验的进出口货物且满足相关条件的；</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4、邮件、快件、暂时进出口货物（含ATA单证册项下货物）、过境货物、中欧班列载运货物、市场采购方式出口货物、跨境电子商务零售进出口商品、免税品以及外交、常驻机构和人员公自用物品。</span></p></span></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">图解：</strong></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，海关取消转关，有什么影响？</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: none; display: inline-block; width: 670px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -2px; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: bold; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.7; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.5; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.3; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span></span></section><section style=\"margin-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对陆路运输业务的影响最为直接</strong></p></section></section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">明年开始，原本只有转关备案的车辆可承接的业务，公告实施起，所有的车辆均可承接业务，不再有制度性的门槛。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其次是操作习惯及操作方式的改变。对进出境监管车辆而言，如习惯于转关操作的，现在大部分将转为通关一体化。但一线口岸业务量增加的情况下如何保证通关效率，这对口岸海关和进出口企业都将是个挑战。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而如果选择跨境通方式，第一，车辆必须要安装电子关锁并备案。第二，目前只有少数二线口岸的系统及设备支持跨境通系统，大部分车检场都需要改造后，才可以使用该系统。这对客户及运输公司来说，也都需要一个适应的过程。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-indent: 0em; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: none; display: inline-block; width: 670px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -2px; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: bold; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.7; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.5; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.3; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span></span></section><section style=\"margin-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对陆路进口报关业务的影响较大</strong></p></section></section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">首先是报关模式的改变。公告实施后，涉及港车及内陆转关的业务将全部转为通关一体化或跨境通。考虑到通关一体化模式仍处于磨合阶段，一旦出现异常，处理起来将会非常困难。而新推出的跨境通系统，也还不够成熟，如无法实现“清单下载”模式来录入报关单，系统故障频次高等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其次是具体操作可能面临比较大的挑战。因公告并未明确取代转关的配套操作细则，某些业务，特别是涉及到特殊监管区的进出口，货物的进出将面临较大的问题。如涉及到特殊监管区之间如何流转的问题，涉及到货物如何进出监管区的卡口及货物如何监管的问题等。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: none; display: inline-block; width: 670px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -2px; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: bold; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.7; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.5; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.3; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span></span></section><section style=\"margin-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">影响报关行的命运</strong></p></section></section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">取消转关对“二线关”如东莞、惠州等地的报关行影响巨大。原来主要依靠在主管海关申报转关业务的二线关的报关行，如果不能转型或改变操作模式，明年将面临无事可做的困境。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: none; display: inline-block; width: 670px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -2px; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: bold; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.7; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.5; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.3; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span></span></section><section style=\"margin-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">利好工厂</strong></p></section></section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">48号公告对内地的工厂来说是个重大利好。取消转关，意味着工厂可以摆脱地方利益的束缚，享受通关一体化带来的贸易便利，免除货物滞留转关场带来的延误，时效大为提升；大幅减少代理报关费用（原来口岸办理转关和主管海关拆关都要产生报关费）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: none; display: inline-block; width: 670px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -2px; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: bold; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.7; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.5; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); font-weight: 700; opacity: 0.3; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&gt;</span></span></section><section style=\"margin-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(233, 131, 109); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">转场将不复存在</strong></p></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">取消转关对转关场才是致命的影响，没有了转关业务，大部分转关场将不复存在。</span></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"87580\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"87665\" style=\"max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\" __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.40816326530612246\" data-src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/8t7hKdPkTGoYAYRvk9MSxoicbkNyXJkITjvmqVTkDoghHdibOpLJWHDhTpFt4iaRsy1XXBlVYst4lrVicXMOfMMVicg/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"49\" title=\"动态分割图\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" data-order=\"0\" style=\"max-width: 100%; display: inline; height: 20px !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 49px !important;\"></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">海关取消转场对运输、报关相关行业冲击巨大，相关企业应如何应对，在此，我们整理了一些应对措施：</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"85866\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、运输</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p></section><ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><li style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">转型，原内陆转关业务转型为非转关业务。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></li><li style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">升级，进出境监管车辆建议尽快升级为电子关锁。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></li><li style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">拓展，由于大量的进出境监管车辆需要处理一线口岸查验等相关业务，可考虑在业务集中的口岸设立服务机构或者寻求优秀的合作伙伴。</span></p></li></ul><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></section><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"85866\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、报关</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p></section><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><li style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">密切联系海关，关注海关操作细则的出台。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></li><li style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">及时向海关和报关协会反映公告执行过程中遇到的问题。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></li><li style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">积极参与，各相关企业应积极尝试新的通关方式，争取又快又平稳地进行业务过渡。</span></p></li><li style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><div><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></div></li></ul><section data-role=\"paragraph\" class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>', null, '2017-12-27 18:47:04', '2017-12-27 19:12:36');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('20', '被海关行政处罚要如何处理？', '10多年专家教教你', '3', '0', '0', null, '2', '3', '1', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_24-5a437b3fb5f5b.png', '0.00', '即将走进职场的你--为职场「人际」「社交」所困扰的你--25/30/35 遇到职场瓶颈的你--对「人的行为」背后的规律感兴趣的你', '0', '<ul style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-position: inside; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">1.角色扮演</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">2.印象管理</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">3.小群体压力</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">4.交换理论</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">5.破窗效应</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">6.邓巴数定律</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">7.弱关系效应</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">8.墨菲定理</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">9.认知失调</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">10.乌合之众</li></ul>', '<div><br></div><div><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 30px; font-size: 14px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">海关行政处罚</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">是指海关根据法律授予的行政处罚权力，对公民、法人或者其他组织违反海关法律、行政法规和规章，依法不追究刑事责任的走私行为和违反海关监管规定的行为，以及法律、行政法规规定由海关实施行政处罚的行为所实施的一种行政制裁。</span></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">由于不了解而被处罚的情况十分常见，小编特整理了一些海关行政处罚中比较常见的问题，并附上对应解答。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62)