idth: 100%; color: rgb(0, 45, 96); line-height: 2.8em; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); color: inherit; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">海关行政处罚怎么申请复议？&nbsp;</span></span></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px auto; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; border: 0px currentcolor; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; border-left: 2px solid rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 4p