tion style=\"max-width: 100%; border: 0px currentcolor; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; border-left: 2px solid rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; margin-left: -35px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 16px; border: 2px solid rgb(0, 45, 96); width: 20px; height: 20px; text-align: center; color: inherit; line-height: 32px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -8px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 45, 96); border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2</span></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: -20px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 45, 96); border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">申请对象</span></span></p></section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; color: inherit; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对海关具体行政行为不服的，向作出该具体行政行为的海关的上一级海关提出行政复议申请；对海关总署作出的具体行政行为不服的，向海关总署提出行政复议申请。</span></span></p></section></section></section></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px auto; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; border: 0px currentcolor; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 25px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; border-left: 2px solid rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 4px; margin-left: -35px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 16px; border: 2px solid rgb(0, 45, 96); width: 20px; height: 20px; text-align: center; color: inherit; line-height: 32px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -8px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 45, 96); border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3</span></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: -20px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 45, 96); border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">申请方式</span></span></p></section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; color: inherit; line-height: 30px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">申请人书面申请行政复议的，可以采取当面递交、邮寄、传真、电子邮件等方式递交行政复议申请书。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">申请人口头申请行政复议的，海关行政复议机构应当当场制作《行政复议申请笔录》交申请人核对或者向申请人宣读，并且由其签字确认。（详见《中华人民共和国海关行政复议办法》）&nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当然，也可以不选择复议直接申请诉讼的哦！&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div><div><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></div>', null, '2017-12-27 18:54:15', '2017-12-27 18:58:37');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('21', '重要消息！国家突然宣布削减关税，多种商品', '你值得拥有', '3', '0', '0', null, '2', '4', '0', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_16-5a437b9a330e7.png', '0.00', '以暂定税率方式降低关税，意味着什么？--未来，这个暂定税率还有一定下调空间。--国家突然宣布削减关税，多种商品受益--部分消费品进口暂定税率调整表--国务院关税税则委员会宣布将从12月1日起，以暂定税率方式降低部分消费品进口关税。--降低消费成本', '0', '<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">查看原公告：<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwNzE3MzE2NQ==&amp;mid=2652787320&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=846cd3289ea0054876eb0f3893d71a1f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(67, 149, 245); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">海关总署公告2017年第57号（关于调整部分消费品进口关税的公告）</a></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2017年11月24日，</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">国务院关税税则委员会宣布将从12月1日起，以暂定税率方式降低部分消费品进口关税。</strong></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这次降低关税，涵盖了食品、保健品、药品、日化用品、</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">衣着鞋帽</strong></span>、<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">家用设备、文化娱乐、日杂百货等各类消费品，</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">共涉及187个8位税号，平均税率由17.3%降至7.7%。</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">业内专家对21世纪经济报道记者表示，降低这些消费品关税，一方面能满足国内居民消费升级的需求，降低进口成本；另一方面也是中国践行贸易自由化的主张，进一步扩大对外开放，让世界更多国家和企业分享到中国经济增长、消费繁荣带来的红利。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><blockquote style=\"padding-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-left: 3px solid rgb(219, 219, 219); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">降低消费成本</span></strong></span></p></blockquote><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我国从2015年以来，已陆续降低了部分服装、箱包、鞋靴、特色食品和药品等消费品的进口关税。</strong></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">国务院关税税则委员会表示，随着社会经济发展、科学技术进步和人口结构变化，人民的消费需求不断升级。此次降低消费品进口关税，紧紧围绕消费需求旺盛、与人民日常生活息息相关、国内一时供给不上的一些优质产品和特色优势产品，有利于丰富国内消费选择，引导国内供给体系转型升级。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">随着国内消费结构的升级，国内居民对品牌、特色商品需求量加大，国内供给存在一定空白，需要扩大进口来加以满足。通过降低关税，能降低进口成本。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">以暂定税率方式降低关税，意味着什么？</strong></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">赵萍表示，暂定税率不是固定的，一段时间后可能会改变。我国加入WTO之后，进口关税在逐年下降。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">未来，这个暂定税率还有一定下调空间</strong></span>。</span></p>', '<blockquote style=\"padding-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-left: 3px solid rgb(219, 219, 219); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">鼓励进口，扩大开放</span></strong></span></p></blockquote><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“这也表明政府贸易政策的转向，从原来的鼓励出口，转为现在同时也鼓励进口”，胡怡建指出。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">中国政府贸易政策确有转向，“促进口”成为重要方面。今年5月份，在“一带一路”国际合作高峰论坛上，中国表示将从2018年起举办中国国际进口博览会。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">7月17日，中央财经领导小组第十六次会议上强调，要在稳定出口市场的同时主动扩大进口，促进经常项目收支平衡。要研究降低有些消费品的关税，鼓励特色优势产品进口。要创造公平竞争的国内市场环境，在关税、进口检验、市场营销等方面创造机会平等的条件，让消费者自主选择，让市场发挥作用。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">关税的职能之一，在于保护国内产业。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">降低关税会对相关产业带来什么影响</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">？</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">赵萍表示，降低关税是为了实现以开放促改革，对国内产品形成竞争，增加国内企业转型升级的压力和动力。这也对外释放信号，未来会有更多商品进入中国，诸如苹果手机、奢侈品箱包等在中国实行撇脂定价策略的进口品牌，他们较高的定价策略也有必要调整，因为商品竞争会更加激烈。</span></p>', null, '2017-12-27 18:54:21', '2017-12-27 19:27:32');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('22', '新分层和集合竞价会带来什么？', '靴子落地', '3', '0', '0', null, '2', '6', '1', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_17-5a437c66aaa84.png', '0.00', '为什么越努力，越焦虑？--怎么防止一步步走向平庸--怎么处理「办公室那点事儿」？--怎么和上级下级沟通--性格不强势的人怎么更好地发展--怎么解决「跳槽也搞不定」的问题', '0', '<ul style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-position: inside; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">《日常生活中的自我呈现》戈夫曼 著</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">《社会心理学》迈尔斯 著</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">《社会生活中的交换和权力》布劳 著</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">《破窗效应》乔治·凯林、凯瑟琳·柯尔 著</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">《你需要多少朋友》罗宾·邓巴 著</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">《找工作：关系人与职业生涯研究》格兰诺威特 著</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">《认知失调理论》费斯汀格教授 著</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">《乌合之众——大众心理研究》勒庞 著</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">《为什么？》查尔斯·蒂利 著</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">《心理暗示与自我暗示》弥儿·柯尓 著</li></ul>', '<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">12</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">月22日，全国股转公司今日在北京召开新三板分层与交易制度改革新闻发布会，并在会上发布了<strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">分层制度的完善、交易制度和信息披露制度改革</span></strong>等内容。这只靴子的落地无疑为新三板市场带来了一丝暖意。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-ad