e=\"margin-top: -1.2em; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; border: none; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 8px 23px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; background-color: rgb(15, 15, 25); border-color: rgb(183, 184, 184); color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">标准三</span></strong></section><section class=\"\" data-style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: left;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\" style=\"padding: 16px 16px 10px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); line-height: 1.4; font-size: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">、最近有成交的60个做市或者竞价转让日的平均市值不少于6亿元；</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">、股本总额不少于5000万元；</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">、采取做市转让方式的，做市商家数不少于6家。</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">另外还有一个共同标准：满足最近12个月完成过股票发行融资，且融资额累计不低于1000万元；合格投资者不少于50人，公司治理健全，财报披露合规等。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">同时在分层制度基础上，新三板将实施创新层企业与基础层差异化的披露要求，创新层公司从严要求，基础层公司继续执行现有规则。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">具体是，创新层公司增加披露季报；预约在次年4月披露年报的创新层企业需在2月底前披露业绩快报；执行财政部关于关键事项审计准则的相关规定。签字注册会计师定期轮换。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对比旧版的分层标准可以发现，股转公司这一次的分层依据做了以下两大调整：首先，在差异化准入标准中，</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">调减净利润标准，提高营业收入标准，新增竞价市值标准；</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其次，着眼于提高创新层公司稳定性，防止“大进大出”，</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">将维持标准改为以合法合规和基本财务要求为主。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">此外，股转公司在创新层的维持标准中设置了</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“合格投资者人数不少于50人”</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">的要求。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><blockquote style=\"margin: 5px auto; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 2em; height: 2em; border: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); transform: rotate(45deg); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 7px; margin-left: -8px; max-width: 100%; width: 2em; height: 2em; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; transform: rotate(-45deg); width: 26px; height: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 19.2px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">02</p></section></section></section></blockquote></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">新标准带来了哪些影响呢？</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">新的分层标准对于财务指标的要求降低了，这可以让更多还在基础层挣扎的企业看到希望，同时，这个标准的设立也为更高层次——精选层的推出预留了空间。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">此外，这一次创新层维持标准的调整也能让创新层的稳定性得到提升，其中，50人的限制条件也为增强新三板流动性起到一定作用。但是，新标准的出台并不意味着明年会出现创新层扩容的情况，创新层企业的质量也并不会下降。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其次，来看一看投资者最关注重点：竞价交易制度的引入。以下两张图非常直白地解释了股转公司此次引入集合竞价制度的具体操作方法。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><blockquote style=\"margin: 5px auto; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 2em; height: 2em; border: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); transform: rotate(45deg); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 7px; margin-left: -8px; max-width: 100%; width: 2em; height: 2em; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; transform: rotate(-45deg); width: 26px; height: 28px; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 19.2px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">03</p></section></section></section></blockquote></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，集合竞价来了，对于新三板企业有什么影响呢？</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">首先，对于投资者来说最大的好处就是<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">股票价格将变得更公允。</span>在集合竞价到来之前，挂牌企业时常会出现市盈率超高或者超低的情况，虽然“异常”价格需要出公告，但是这样的监管形式并不能从根源上解决问题。集合竞价的推出从股票价格公允性的角度来看是非常大的进步。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其次，集合竞价真的能带来流动性吗？这其实也要分情况讨论。<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对于新三板中的佼佼者来说，集合竞价给了他们不小的舞台，</span>能帮助他们吸引到更多的资金，流动性自然会更强。但是相对的，一些表现平平的新三板企业能得到的投资机会会更少。无论是机构投资者还是个人投资者，都将更愿意购入到创新层的好企业，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对于不能进入创新层的企业来说，每天仅一次的集合竞价机会对本就不足的流动性将有不小打击。</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">新三板改革的前菜已经端上来了，主菜何时送上？我们拭目以待。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p>', null, '2017-12-27 18:59:32', '2017-12-28 14:19:15');
