100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(172, 29, 16); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-bottom: -10px; padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(172, 29, 16); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); min-width: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">印尼海关退证频发成企业出口拦路虎</span></p></section></section></section><section style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-right: 1px solid rgb(172, 29, 16); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(172, 29, 16); transform: rotate(45deg); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">今年1-11月，浙江湖州检验检疫局收到来自印尼海关的原产地证退证查询函52份，同比增长226％。值得注意的是，印尼海关今年的退证查询量占湖州地区退证查询总量的96%，部分货物证书在我方未回函前就已被勾选“不可享受关税减免”标记，对湖州企业开拓印尼市场的阻碍影响不容小觑。&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">中国-东盟自贸区原产地证，是符合中国原产标准的货物在输往东南亚市场时证明“籍贯”的文件。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">持有该证书可使产品在东盟范围内享受关税减免优惠政策，有效提高出口商品的竞争力，是名副其实的“纸黄金”。据了解，来自印尼海关的“退证查询函”所查询的内容主要集中在<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">质疑原产地证标准、产品是否符合直运规则以及原产地证书内容与发票内容不符等方面。</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">印尼海关频繁退证查询对湖企出口影响甚大。以所退证书中一家生产商标带的公司为例，该公司近3万美元的产品本可享受货值5%的关税减免，但因所申请的中国-东盟自贸区优惠原产地证书被印尼海关退证查询并被采取取消关税优惠的措施，收货人不得不缴纳1500美元关税，企业利益受到严重损害。另外一家企业连续3批货物遭到质疑是否符合直运规则的调查，对货物通关和后续征税方面也造成了负面影响。&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">针对这一情况，湖州局迅速采取一系列措施帮助企业积极应对：第一时间对辖区内所有出口企业发出警示，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">通报印尼海关最新动向，</span>并强调近期签证需注意的要点。<span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">加强业务指导，对企业所申报的货物品名、原产地标准、运输路线填写等方面进行指导，避免因证书填制不详等问题引发对方退证查询。</span>做好退证复函工作，与被调查企业积极联动，缩短调查时间，避免出口货物长时间在国外口岸滞港，降低直接经济损失。&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><blockquote style=\"margin: 5px auto; max-width: 100%; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 40px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); display: inline-block; height: 40px; line-height: 40px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"padding-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">也 门</span></strong></p></section></section></blockquote></section><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-bottom: -14px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(172, 29, 16); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-bottom: -10px; padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(172, 29, 16); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); min-width: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); min-width: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">赫伯罗特、APL</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">相继发布通知停止接受到也门货物运输</span></p></section></section></section><section style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-right: 1px solid rgb(172, 29, 16); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(172, 29, 16); transform: rotate(45deg); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">12月21日，赫伯罗特发布通知，禁止了一些货物向也门运输。此通知即日起效，赫伯罗特将停止接受以下货物向也门运输的预订：</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">武器、爆炸物、化肥、防弹车、钢管、摩托车及摩托车零配件、车辆及零配件、危险品、电池、化学物品。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">12月20日，APL发布通知，由于近期中东内部的政治冲突，导致也门的港口不确定能否继续开放。因此<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">将立即停止接受预定到也门的亚丁港和荷台达的商业货物的新订单。</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">重新接受日期将另行通知。通知内容如下：</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">据悉，自今年也门政治冲突爆发以来，其国内港口就被关闭，后虽有短暂开放，但是往来商业船只和货物的安全仍不能被完全保障。加之其国内港口停泊授权的不确定性，导致许多海运货物运输被迫中断。&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">此前，马士基就因也门国内的战乱原因停止了到荷台达港口的货物的预订。&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果也门一直持续这样的局面，肯定会对出口贸易造成极大的影响。近期有出货到也门的货主们请注意船公司发布的通知，及早做两手准备，以备不时之需。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p></div>', null, '2017-12-27 19:04:47', '2017-12-28 10:18:52');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('24', '关于AEO认证的干货全在这里！', '想通过AEO认证的企业赶紧来看看！', '2', '0', '0', '1', '1', '5', '0', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_26-5a437e86b23ed.png', '0.01', '想通过AEO认证的企业赶紧来看看！--关于AEO认证的干货全在这里！', '0', '<p style=\"margin-top: 2px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">前段时间在一家工厂做报告说明时，听到管理人员说，一直以为AEO是报关搞搞就好了，哪知还涉及企业内部管理。没错！AEO在某种程度上说就是工厂的CEO，是包括报关在内的工厂多部门的规范。我在2010年左右开始帮助一些企业申请A及AA，那时我将其归纳成硬件和软件两个方面，也许报关主导搞搞就好，但现如今看来，已基本都是软件了，必须是公司内部多部门的规范并落实实施才能通过。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“AEO不是ISO，是要真正规范及落实实施，要切实的帮助企业获取更多的便利”</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">，我们已经多次在工厂的复审现场听到海关如是叮咛。</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（P.S.在这里没有贬低ISO的意思，只是有些企业不认真落实实施，流于形式，套用标准，拿证为目的，导致现在口碑越来越不好了。）</span></p>', '<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">从2014年年底到现在都接近3年了，却依然有企业对AEO一知半解甚至误解，还停留在拿“牌照”的阶段。当然这也不能全怪企业，AEO认证本来就是一个管理的系统工程，有时候管理者很可能会被一两个法规带入理解的误区。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所有，今天我要给大家详细的说说AEO这个一直为大家所关注、又爱又恨的关键词，如若您能看到结尾，对您有所帮助，那就是我的荣幸了！</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">说明</span>：本文涉及绝大部分图表都为本人制作，转载或引用请注明出处）。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86125\" data-color=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" data-custom=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 1em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding: 15px 2px; max-width: 100%; width: 3.5em; height: 2.5em; display: inline-block; text-align: center; line-height: 0.8em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 32px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1</span></section><section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: -3.1em; margin-left: 2.5em; padding: 15px 15px 15px 35px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 3.5em; border: 1px solid rgb(33, 33, 34); color: rgb(33, 33, 34); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">发展历程</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">AEO的发展历程有两条线路，一条是国家诚信体系建设，另一条是WCO（世界海关组织）。这两条路中关于海关AEO，是殊途同归的。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86269\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 2px solid rgb(153, 153, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 28px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.2 WCO（世界海关组织）</span></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">WCO（World Customs Organization）是世界范围的专门研究海关事务的国际政府间组织，它的使命是：加强各成员海关工作效益和提高海关工作效率，促进各成员在海关执法领域的合作。2005年6月，WCO通过了《全球贸易安全与便利标准框架》，中国积极响应倡议，在会上签署了实施《标准框架》的意向书，并最终发展到现在的<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3ODAxOTExMw==&amp;mid=203717236&amp;idx=4&amp;sn=ab8fa172ac6432e5fe3bc512750580d3&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(67, 149, 245); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">海关总署225号令</a>（<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">点击蓝色字体查看原公告</span>）。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">截止2014年7月，WCO的179个成员中已有168个签署了实施《全球贸易安全与便利标准框架》意向书，53个经济体建立了AEO制度（包括中国、美国、欧盟、日本、韩国、新加坡等）。（说明：这些信息和数据来自网络，未找到确切来源，如果涉及版权，请告知我登记来源）</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">注释</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">：</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">什么是AEO？</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">经认证的经营者（Authorized Economic Operation）：在世界海关组织（WCO）制定的《全球贸易安全与便利标准框架》中被定义为：“以任何一种方式参与货物国际流通，并被海关当局认定符合世界海关组织或相应供应链安全标准的一方，包括生产商、进口商、出口商、报关行、承运商、理货人、中间商、口岸和机场、货站经营者、综合经营者、仓储业经营者和分销商”。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">下面我依然按时间的顺序整理了一段历程，如下图二。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 11px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（图二：海关总署225号令的进程）</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">另外，自从一带一路的概念出来后，AEO的推广又逐步和一带一路挂上钩了，就在11月9日“海关发布”公众号上还发表了题为：“<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwNzE3MzE2NQ==&amp;mid=2652786969&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1f5709c2a6cce84208f456abc1841089&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(67, 149, 245); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">中以签署海关AEO互认安排 促进“一带一路”贸易便利化</a>”的文章。（<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">点击蓝色字体查看原文章</span>）</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">不管是从上述国家诚信体系建设，还是从WCO的发展框架，亦或从是一带一路的布局来看，在中国的企业，规范管理推动AEO认证已是大势所趋，<strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">企业要做的就是顺势而为，跟上发展潮流，而不是被时代淘汰。</strong></span></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86125\" data-color=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" data-custom=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 1em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding: 15px 2px; max-width: 100%; width: 3.5em; height: 2.5em; display: inline-block; text-align: center; line-height: 0.8em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 32px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2</span></section><section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: -3.1em; margin-left: 2.5em; padding: 15px 15px 15px 35px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 3.5em; border: 1px solid rgb(33, 33, 34); color: rgb(33, 33, 34); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">企业收获</section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86269\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 2px solid rgb(153, 153, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 28px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.2 国内便利</span><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-left: 5px; padding-right: 4px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; text-transform: uppercase; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这里我分三个方面说明一下，一个是法规中有明确规定的（海关总署225号令），第二是国家一直在推广的联合激励，第三是联合惩戒。不过在说这三个方面之前，我要说一下海关总署225号令跟原来的197号令的一些差异，您会感觉到国家对企业的诚意，感受到便利与公平正义。为了不至于让大家看文字看得疲惫，我这里直接汇总了一个EXCEL图表，具体如下图三。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 11px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（图三：225号令与197号令比较图）</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">从这个图表上，您可看到国家已经取消了企业规模大小、企业设立时间长短、以及涉及知识产权的限制，真正的体现了公平正义，申请AEO认证获得高信用评价，也不再是大企业、老企业才可以的了。而且企业认证不通过的话还有90天的改善期（当然有几个关键指标是不在此90天的改善之列的），海关是想真正的帮助企业的（而不是像ISO一样套标准或报关员搞搞就行的）。也不像原来一样，必须逐级申请，现在只要您的条件符合，可以越级直接申请最高级别的认证，更加人性化和便利。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"90150\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"padding-left: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; width: 469px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px 10px; border-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(197, 36, 36); border-left-color: rgb(197, 36, 36); border-right-color: rgb(197, 36, 36); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.2.1 法规明确规定的便利</p></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在海关总署的第225号令中，有明确说明AEO一般认证企业和高级认证企业可以享受的各种优惠，这里我直接上图表给大家看看（如下图四）。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 11px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（图四：一般认证企业和高级认证企业的优惠比较图）</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其实法规内的只是一个框架，国家在推行很多新的便利或操作方法时，通常是需要企业达到一定级别的，比如现在推行的以企业为单元的监管，就需要企业达到一般认证企业的管理级别，再比如现在推行的汇总征税，如果是失信企业就不能参与。而目前海关的整体形势就是要改革与发展，所以我们也只有尽快申请通过AEO认证才能跟上海关的步伐。</span></p><div><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></div>', null, '2017-12-27 19:07:09', '2017-12-27 19:13:28');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('25', '集装箱运输产业智能化还会远吗？', '工业4.0已在路上', '2', '0', '0', '2', '1', '3', '0', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_30-5a437f51ac5ca.png', '0.01', '当职场难题遇上社会学--角色扮演：设定并经营你的职场人设--从众行为：不要做团队的「平均人」--交换理论：获取最大回报的底层逻辑', '0', '<ul style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-position: inside; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">怎样适应陌生的工作环境？</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">怎么面对批评？</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">怎么控制我们的工作情绪？</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">为什么越努力越焦虑？</li></ul>', '<div><br></div><div><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; transform: rotate(0deg); width: 134px; height: 5px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; height: 5px; background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><section style=\"margin-top: -5px; padding: 20px; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 26.25px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">近期麦肯锡发布研究报告<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（点击底部阅读原文，可查看报告摘要）</span>表示，随着数字科技、大数据和物联网(IoT)时代的来临，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">集装箱运输业在未来50年内可能面临冲击，需采取必要的因应措施。</span></span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">研究报告指出，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在未来的50年内，海上将充斥着大量的自动化20尺标准集装箱(TEU)，或是一种类似于模块化、像无人机般的漂浮集装箱，具备自动化的运输供应链，并且由无人机来进行最后一里的交付任务。</span>届时，这种集装箱的贸易量将可能会增长为当前的2～5倍左右。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">受到全球自动化和机器人技术的日趋普及影响，航运业的短程运输量预料也将会随之增加。另外，未来远东地区的集装箱运输流量则可望继续保持相对大量的水平，而<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">全球第二大的重点贸易路线将可能会以南亚作为中继站，并且连结至非洲大陆。</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在历经过了数次高度破坏性的产能过剩和产业整合的周期后，未来集装箱航运产业将可能会催生出3～4家新兴的大型航运企业。这些企业主要会是一种具备强大客户导向，具有独立的数字技术优势和创新的商业运作模式，也可能会是拥有强大数字和实体资源兼备的科技巨头公司旗下的小型分支企业。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">分析师预测，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">未来50年内，传统只经营独立货运业务的公司将会面临全数被淘汰的命运，因为数字化互动带来的冲击将会使中介商的存在不再被需要。</span>而所有存留下来的航运企业，势必都将会透过数据生态系统而紧密的互相链接，与客户之间的互动和企业营运系统也将会完全被数字化。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对于整体成长状况不断减缓的集装箱航运产业而言，这样的愿景和变化，恐怕将是一场令人望而生畏的改变过程。对此，麦肯锡建议，航运公司可考虑从三方面着手布局。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">首先，</span></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">航运公司应借助投资数字化技术来实现其产品与价值链的差异化，从而改善其客户服务质量、提高生产力、以及降低营运成本。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其次，</span></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">便是进行新一轮的整合，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">因为下一代的创新将不得不在整个产业价值链上进行必要的策划与重整。</span>届时，运输业者与终端营运商将共享更大的船只、码头的基础建设投资、透明化的船舶行程信息，以及更大型的集装箱等等。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">最后，</span></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">同时也是最关键的部分，除了远见，企业还必须具备采取行动的胆识。一如航运产业是建立在充满风暴之中的航程旅途之上，尽管目前的航运产业正面临着一波波的逆风来袭，尤其是数字科技风潮，而那些敢于抓住先机的企业，才有可能成为未来的最大赢家。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></p></div>', null, '2017-12-27 19:09:54', '2017-12-27 19:12:09');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('26', '跨境电商物流的清关风', '从英国查验的套路浅析', '2', '0', '0', '1', '1', '6', '1', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_6-5a4380c0cfad7.png', '0.01', '书本知识：体系陈旧、更新慢，无法预测新趋势；--新闻资讯：系统性差，太局限，内容质量没保证。', '0', '<ul style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-position: inside; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">比特币、区块链的技术原理</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">系统了解比特币及其实操注意事项</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">掌握虚拟货币全球政策和市场情况</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">区块链对经济金融、银行、投资领域 1-5 年后的影响</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">区块链的最新进展和应用趋势</li></ul>', '<div><br></div><div><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-left: 15px; padding: 3px; max-width: 100%; width: 40px; height: 40px; border: 2px solid rgb(226, 86, 27); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; transform: rotateZ(0deg); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 30px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; transform: rotate(0deg); background-color: rgb(226, 86, 27); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><section style=\"margin-top: -18px; padding: 23px 15px 15px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 2px solid rgb(226, 86, 27); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">近期，有卖家反馈货物在英国海关遭遇“多次查验”——海关通知查验后放行，没几天又收到查验通知。对此，经过与海外清关行沟通，小编梳理了一下英国的查验套路，并对跨境电商货物的清关风险作了简单分析。</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">整个2017年闹得沸沸扬扬的欧洲VAT，在欧盟针对电商行业优化VAT注册申报体系的一系列措施中，仿佛有了定论，但是新的税务监管措施要到2019-2021年才逐步落地执行。<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2018-2019年的过渡期间，欧洲的清关或许仍将让跨境电商卖家和物流服务商头疼。</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 1em auto; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; transform: rotate(45deg); width: 60px; line-height: 60px; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid rgb(72, 115, 114); height: 60px; color: rgb(254, 254, 254); background-color: rgb(119, 170, 169); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; transform: rotate(-45deg); font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">01</span></section></section><section style=\"padding-left: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-bottom: -1px; padding-bottom: 5px; max-width: 100%; width: 210px; overflow: hidden; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(105, 105, 105); font-size: 20px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">谁来查</span></strong></section><section style=\"padding-top: 5px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">海关的职能划分与风险管控设计</span></span></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">英国海关职能主要由皇家税务与海关署（HMRC）行使，下属的税局、边防、商检等部门各司其职，整体覆盖税收征收职能与监管与缉私职能。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">各部门协同管理，在日常工作中有非常紧密的业务联系。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">英国海关风险管理机构分为中央和地方两个层级，边境管理署国家情报信息中心属于中央层级，地方层级是设置在口岸海关的风险管理分中心，包括情报信息分中心与风险布控分中心，各分中心设置若干情报信息组和风险布控组。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">全国范围内的情报信息组和风险布控组，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">根据运输渠道与监管项目两条主线，分别形成了一个类矩阵式结构体系。</span>各个情报信息组与风险布控组的配置由相关项目的业务特点和业务量等决定。例如集装箱业务量占英国65%的费利克斯托港海关，在相关配置上更严谨。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">英国海关海量的数据积累，使得英国海关可以轻易的利用数据对比的方式找出那些数据申报异于平常的货物。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 1em auto; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; transform: rotate(45deg); width: 60px; line-height: 60px; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid rgb(72, 115, 114); height: 60px; color: rgb(254, 254, 254); background-color: rgb(119, 170, 169); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; transform: rotate(-45deg); font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">02</span></section></section><section style=\"padding-left: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-bottom: -1px; padding-bottom: 5px; max-width: 100%; width: 165px; overflow: hidden; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(105, 105, 105); font-size: 20px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">怎么</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span>查</span></strong></section><section style=\"padding-top: 5px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">大数据支持下的风险预判</span></span></span></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">基于长期积累和沉淀的数据，英国海关对于进口货物的管控已经从人工临检逐步升级为系统智能化设计。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">针对申报进口的货物，有管控权限的各部门(税局, 边防, 商检)可以根据自己的需要提前在海关系统中备注，哪一些货品最近抽查比例需要提高等。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">根据这些数据和备注，海关系统会自动判断货物是否符合查验要求，并扣货和通知相关部门来检查相关的货物。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">常见的扣货部门会针对不同情况扣货。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 5px auto; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-left: 25px; max-width: 100%; background-image: url(&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/tWGod0QyJPjPGFyRfGq516sEkD5k0QTrqCdCXLfZDjenM9vichuAMc6n4IFconibnOgroZsVArNQHu3iboWOvPoTw/0?wx_fmt=gif&quot;); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 28px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">TS - TRADING STANDARD&nbsp;：</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">相当于国内的质量检查委员会，</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">会针对近期重点监控的商品作相对应的关于商品使用安全的检查。</span></p></section><section style=\"padding-left: 25px; max-width: 100%; background-image: url(&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/tWGod0QyJPjPGFyRfGq516sEkD5k0QTrqCdCXLfZDjenM9vichuAMc6n4IFconibnOgroZsVArNQHu3iboWOvPoTw/0?wx_fmt=gif&quot;); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 28px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">Border Force-</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">相当于国内的边防，</span>检查扣货的原因通常是，怀疑走私。</span></p></section><section style=\"padding-left: 25px; max-width: 100%; background-image: url(&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/tWGod0QyJPjPGFyRfGq516sEkD5k0QTrqCdCXLfZDjenM9vichuAMc6n4IFconibnOgroZsVArNQHu3iboWOvPoTw/0?wx_fmt=gif&quot;); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 28px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">PortHealth -</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">相当于国内的检验检疫局。</span>任何怀疑含有动物或相关成分，并对人体造成影响的商品都会受到检查，如皮鞋刷中是否含有动物毛或者胶囊中是否含有动物内脏或相关成份等。</span></p></section></ul></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">大部分情况下，都是其中一个部门查验通过后即可放行，但是，偶尔遇到高风险或者政策高度关注的货物，也会出现一个部门刚查完放行，另一个部门接着通知查验的情况。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 1em auto; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; transform: rotate(45deg); width: 60px; line-height: 60px; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid rgb(72, 115, 114); height: 60px; color: rgb(254, 254, 254); background-color: rgb(119, 170, 169); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; transform: rotate(-45deg); font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">03</span></section></section><section style=\"padding-left: 1.5em; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-bottom: -1px; padding-bottom: 5px; max-width: 100%; width: 165px; overflow: hidden; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(105, 105, 105); font-size: 20px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">清关风险</span></strong></section><section style=\"padding-top: 5px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(105, 105, 105); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">跨境电商货物的清关风险</span></span></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">近年来跨境电商快速发展，在跨国贸易中成为举足轻重的贸易方式，但是，因为跨境电商通常是直接针对C端进行全流程设计，与传统贸易的B2B相比，其整个贸易链末端的目的国进口清关、派送等环节，均没有可以直接套用的管控模式。</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">跨境电商整个环节中，制造和销售往往不会有很大问题，却是在物流运输环节成为较大的风险点</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">——无论是从工厂到目的国的进口，还是目的国的仓储派送，甚至于未售完产品的退货、退运，都成为跨境电商这种贸易形式的难点和痛点。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而对于物流服务商而言，进口国的清关问题则成为决定生死的关键。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">一是部分卖家对于进口国的监管条件了解较少，</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">一些禁止进口或者有条件进口的货物，没有提前了解，导致海关查验和扣货高发。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">二是税务问题混乱，</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">长期以来的“双清包税”做法，使得本应该成为纳税责任人的卖家，长期依赖物流服务商解决税务问题，对相关税费的核算不甚精通。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">无论是前者还是后者，都使得清关成为物流服务商面临的问题。<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而最大的变数，却是在于进口国的政策变化之中。</span></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，当一个国家的进口政策产生变化、尤其是政策收紧的时候，对于物流服务商而言，往往就意味着风险增大。</span></p></div>', null, '2017-12-27 19:19:21', '2018-01-08 15:29:29');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('27', '企业如何做好AEO认证', '做AEO认证，企业到底要做什么？', '3', '0', '1', null, '2', '2', '6', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_13-5a438193abcfb.png', '0.00', '做AEO认证，企业到底要做什么？--企业如何做好AEO认证--AEO实施计划--高层的重视或主导成立AEO认证小组', '0', '<section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86125\" data-color=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" data-custom=\"rgb(33, 33, 34)\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 1em; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: -3.1em; margin-left: 2.5em; padding: 15px 15px 15px 35px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 3.5em; border: 1px solid rgb(33, 33, 34); color: rgb(33, 33, 34); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">企业如何做好AEO认证</section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这一部分也许是真正落实做事的同志们最关注的了。网上也有不少专门做AEO认证的机构或个人，他们都总结了很多。这里我说说我个人的实施经历。不过在说这个之前，企业要明确，做AEO，到底要做什么？</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86269\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 2px solid rgb(153, 153, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 28px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"padding-right: 12px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(108, 124, 156); height: 1.3em; display: inline-block; background-image: url(&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/8t7hKdPkTGpQOzuFnYftEkjdHibNsobr3pnLzWkmTBnSafh0zeribv7aVCXmq7SXhe29wZL1N51BE5sDbvW1D2aA/0?wx_fmt=png&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 100% 12px; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.1 做AEO认证，企业到底要做什么？</span></p></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">做AEO认证，企业到底要做什么？其中一般AEO认证涉及的标准有：共5大类18条29项。而高级AEO认证涉及的标准有：共5大类18条32项。这五大类就是：内部控制、财务状况、守法规范、贸易安全和附加标准。企业做AEO认证，就是要规范前面4大类。网上已有不少总结，这里我换个思路从一般认证企业的角度，来举例说明企业要完成的工作。具体如下图十一、图十二、图十三。</span></p>', '<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">再强调一下，AEO要做的不仅仅是上述内容，最重要的还是这些内容的落实实施，并真正的帮助企业规范管理。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">从上述三个图片不难看出AEO是一个涉及多部门的复杂的规范体系，这里举例如图十四。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 11px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（图十四：AEO是一个涉及多部门的综合规范工作）</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86269\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 2px solid rgb(153, 153, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 28px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"padding-right: 12px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(108, 124, 156); height: 1.3em; display: inline-block; background-image: url(&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/8t7hKdPkTGpQOzuFnYftEkjdHibNsobr3pnLzWkmTBnSafh0zeribv7aVCXmq7SXhe29wZL1N51BE5sDbvW1D2aA/0?wx_fmt=png&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 100% 12px; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.2 AEO诊断</span></p></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">明白AEO认证大概要做些什么事情后，首先要做的就是企业诊断，结合82号公告的附件，以及AEO的内审要求进行。判断哪些是需要规范改善的事项，制作详细的AEO诊断报告，这里我就不再贴范例了。我们东华诊断过的AEO企业已经很多了。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86269\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 2px solid rgb(153, 153, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 28px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"padding-right: 12px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(108, 124, 156); height: 1.3em; display: inline-block; background-image: url(&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/8t7hKdPkTGpQOzuFnYftEkjdHibNsobr3pnLzWkmTBnSafh0zeribv7aVCXmq7SXhe29wZL1N51BE5sDbvW1D2aA/0?wx_fmt=png&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 100% 12px; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.3 AEO实施计划</span></p></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">根据AEO诊断的结果，制定具体的AEO实施计划。我也偷懒不贴范例了。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86269\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 2px solid rgb(153, 153, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 28px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"padding-right: 12px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(108, 124, 156); height: 1.3em; display: inline-block; background-image: url(&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/8t7hKdPkTGpQOzuFnYftEkjdHibNsobr3pnLzWkmTBnSafh0zeribv7aVCXmq7SXhe29wZL1N51BE5sDbvW1D2aA/0?wx_fmt=png&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 100% 12px; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.4 高层的重视或主导成立AEO认证小组</span></p></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">因为AEO认证是涉及公司多部门的全面规范工作，所以必须由公司高层主导成立AEO小组。而且小组成员的骨干力量必须是各部门的主管，另外由主管指定相应的具体对接人员。这样上中下三个层级都是通的，以便于快速落实实施。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">关于认证小组的组织结构，您只需把现有组织图中的部门主管及他的管理者（总经理）拉出来，然后再会议讨论确定下一级具体操作责任人就可以了，我这里不做具体说明。有了这个小组，才能保证AEO实施计划的有效落实。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86269\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 2px solid rgb(153, 153, 153); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 28px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"padding-right: 12px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3em; color: rgb(108, 124, 156); height: 1.3em; display: inline-block; background-image: url(&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/8t7hKdPkTGpQOzuFnYftEkjdHibNsobr3pnLzWkmTBnSafh0zeribv7aVCXmq7SXhe29wZL1N51BE5sDbvW1D2aA/0?wx_fmt=png&quot;); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 100% 12px; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.5 AEO的维护</span></p></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">并不是AEO认证通过后，就可以不管了，高级AEO认证每三年复审一次、一般AEO认证不定期复审，企业内部资金也要每年复审。要根据已经形成的规范持续实施。</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">关于AEO实施，我这里说是的一般套路，每个企业有各自的特点，如有需要我们可以针对性的单独探讨！</span></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"87953\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">最后，祝您在AEO认证的路上越走越好！</span></p>', null, '2017-12-27 19:19:43', '2018-01-08 15:28:51');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('28', '加工贸易台帐保证金制度将退出历史舞台', '过渡期结束后怎么办', '1', '0', '0', null, '3', '5', '5', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_20-5a438339630f3.png', '0.00', '成为比特币&区块链行家，抢占红利--人类社会货币的演变--人类社会货币的演变--比特币转账运行的原理', '1', '<ul style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-position: inside; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">比特币爱好者、数字货币从业者</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">新技术爱好者、技术从业人士</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">对未来有规划的程序员</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">找方向的创业者和投资人</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">保险、证券等相关行业从业人员</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">渴望把握未来先机，做出正确选择的人</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">有追求的经济、金融领域从业者</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">对世界好奇，对趋势敏感的人</li></ul>', '<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-size: 20px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">海关总署公告</span>2017<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年第</span>62<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: inherit; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">号</span></span></strong></section><section style=\"margin: 2px 1em; max-width: 100%; border: 0px rgb(33, 33, 34); font-size: 12px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 2px; padding-right: 2px; padding-left: 2px; max-width: 100%; width: 258.391px; border-top: 3px solid rgb(33, 33, 34); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(33, 33, 34); display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section style=\"margin-right: 2px; margin-left: 2px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%; font-style: italic; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></em></span></section></section><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">关于全面取消加工贸易台帐保证金制度过渡期结束后有关业务办理事宜的公告</span></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-bottom: -8px; margin-left: 20px; max-width: 100%; transform: rotate(0deg); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-width: 2px 2px 0px 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); transform: rotate(-45deg); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: -2px; margin-left: auto; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; border: 2px solid rgb(0, 45, 96); color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); line-height: 30px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">为落实国务院取消加工贸易银行保证金台帐制度（以下简称“保证金台帐”）有关要求，现就海关总署、商务部公告</span>2017<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年第</span>33<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">号设置的过渡期结束后，有关业务办理事宜公告如下：</span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">一、<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">保证金台帐“实转”管理事项转为海关事务担保事项。</span>企业不再到银行开设保证金台帐，按海关事务担保事项办理有关手续。</span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">二、<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对以保证金形式提供担保的，担保事项解除后，企业凭财务收据到主管海关办理保证金及利息退还手续。</span>利息计算利率为中国人民银行公布的活期基准利率，计息起始日期为保证金交至海关指定账户之日，截止日期为海关保证金退还通知书开出之日。</span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">本公告自</span>2018<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年</span>2<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">月</span>2<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">日起执行。</span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">特此公告。</span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: right; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">海关总署</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: right; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2017<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年</span>12<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">月</span>14<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">日</span></span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">看完这则公告，也许有人会觉得很奇怪，为什么海关要取消保证金台账制度，并于2018年2月1日以后退出历史舞台呢？</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><h2 class=\"\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 45, 96); line-height: 32px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、有利于降低制度性交易成本，为企业减负增效</span></h2></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">按现行规定，企业首次办理加工贸易业务时，须事先到银行开设保证金台帐账户，以后办理加工贸易手册时，再到银行设立（变更）保证金台帐，银行每次收取</span>100<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">元手续费（银行对部分优质企业会减免手续费）。</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">保证金台帐制度取消后，对保证金台帐“空转”管理的企业，无须到银行办理任何台帐保证金手续。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">按照</span>2015<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年保证金台帐开设笔数测算，“空转”保证金台帐占总数的</span>95.7%<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">。预计每年可为全国加工贸易企业节省</span>1400<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">万元银行保证金手续费。</span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><h2 class=\"\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 45, 96); line-height: 32px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、有利于监管执法统一，规范海关事务担保管理</span>&nbsp;</span></h2></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">目前，海关向加工贸易企业收取担保的方式有两种，一是保证金台帐制度，二是海关事务担保。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">《中华人民共和国海关加工贸易货物监管办法》（海关总署令第</span>219<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">号）、《中华人民共和国海关关于加工贸易边角料、剩余料件、残次品、副产品和受灾保税货物的管理办法》（海关总署令第</span>111<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">号，经海关总署令第</span>218<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">号修订）等海关规章中</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">明确对加工贸易手册设立、外发加工、余料结转等环节中的高风险情事，企业须提供的担保，具体收取、退还、转税均按照《中华人民共和国海关事务担保条例》（国务院令第</span>581<span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">号）办理。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">保证金台帐和海关事务担保事项在账户设置、保证金征收、退还、转税等属于不同的管理体系。将保证金台帐“实转”调整为海关事务担保事项，有利于统一规范海关事务担保事项。</span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><h2 class=\"\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 45, 96); line-height: 32px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、加工贸易保税监管制度逐步完善，为取消保证金台帐制度创造条件</span>&nbsp;</h2></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">多年来，针对加工贸易保税业务总量大、链条长、环节多、风险高等特点，以《中华人民共和国海关法》《中华人民共和国进出口关税条例》为上位法，海关通过制定和完善部门规章，形成了较为严密的加工贸易监管法律法规规章体系。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">同时，不断优化信息化系统，已实现对加工贸易手册设立、进出口通关、单耗、深加工结转、外发加工、联网监管、边角料处置、内销征税、核销、核查等加工贸易各环节实施全过程监管。加上，</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">由于多数加工贸易业务按规定实施“空转”，保证金台帐制度监管作用日益弱化。</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></span></span></p>', null, '2017-12-27 19:27:26', '2017-12-28 14:07:20');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('29', '读懂“减免税无纸化申报改革”的精髓', '老关务带路！教教你', '1', '0', '0', null, '3', '4', '10', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_14-5a4383f281c04.png', '0.00', '比特币、区块链的技术原理--系统了解比特币及其实操注意事项--掌握虚拟货币全球政策和市场情况--区块链对经济金融、银行、投资领域 1-5 年后的影响--区块链的最新进展和应用趋势', '0', '<ol style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-position: outside; padding-left: 1.4em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><li>1.书本知识：体系陈旧、更新慢，无法预测新趋势；</li><li>2.新闻资讯：系统性差，太局限，内容质量没保证。</li></ol>', '<div><br></div><div><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-left: 15px; padding: 3px; max-width: 100%; width: 40px; height: 40px; border: 2px solid rgb(226, 86, 27); border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; transform: rotateZ(0deg); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 30px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; transform: rotate(0deg); background-color: rgb(226, 86, 27); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><section style=\"margin-top: -18px; padding: 23px 15px 15px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 2px solid rgb(226, 86, 27); font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">哇噻！海关改革的火车是越跑越快，为了提高通关效率，推出了减免税无纸申报。为了便于大家更好的读懂海关总署发布的“关于推广减免税申请无纸化及取消减免税备案的公告”</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">?</span><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MjQzNzE1Mg==&amp;mid=2247489630&amp;idx=3&amp;sn=1b7353425a41c8272fff301b4f0e54ef&amp;chksm=e9e2ef91de956687f99d694c0b550e8d2e00bc7fe3e0ccc72e06c6a851dc2a608cb17b0923ad&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 127, 166); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（海关总署2017年第58号公告）</span></a><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">，笔者经过与广州开发区海关综合业务科、总关减免税科沟通确认，对公告中的几个疑问做了梳理和总结。 &nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 4px; padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 4px; max-width: 100%; border-top-width: 2px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -8px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; float: left; width: 60px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: table; width: 60px; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: table-cell; line-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; font-style: italic; font-size: 42px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1</em></section></section></section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 45, 96); float: left; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">流程</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">自2017年12月15日起，在全国海关推广减免税申请无纸化，但未取消纸质申请模式，即两种模式都可以。</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">因无纸模式对上传资料的要求比较高（主要是针对随附资料页数比较多的情况），难免会出现退单重新上传资料的情况，目前开发海关综合业务科和总关减免税科建议以有纸模式为主。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果采用无纸申报，海关也有可能根据实际需要要求企业提供纸质资料。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 4px; padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 4px; max-width: 100%; border-top-width: 2px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -8px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; float: left; width: 60px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: table; width: 60px; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: table-cell; line-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; font-style: italic; font-size: 42px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2</em></section></section></section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 45, 96); float: left; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">备案</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">大家请注意，<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">公告提到的“取消减免税备案”并不是说可以不用备案就办理免表，而是改变了以往必须先备案后才能申请免表的模式。</span>申请人可在首次办理进口货物减免税手续时一并向海关提交涉及主体资格、项目资质、免税进口额度（数量）等信息相关材料，无需提前单独向海关办理政策项目备案，即减免税备案和免表可以同时递单申请；<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">已备案的减免税项目不需重新办理备案，如需申请免表选择无纸或有纸模式申请即可。</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">取消减免税备案并不是说不用备案，只是说无需提前单独，并没有说不用哦！</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 4px; padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 4px; max-width: 100%; border-top-width: 2px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -8px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; float: left; width: 60px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: table; width: 60px; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: table-cell; line-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; font-style: italic; font-size: 42px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3</em></section></section></section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 45, 96); float: left; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">上传单证的标准、内容&nbsp;</span></strong></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">上传资料的内容：&nbsp;</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（一）随附单证中涉及<span style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">申请人主体资格、免税额度（数量）以及进口商业发票等，应全文上传。&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（二）进口合同页数较多的，含有买卖双方及进口代理人的基本信息，进口货物的名称、规格型号、技术参数、单价及总价、生产国别，合同随附的供货清单，运输方式及付款条件，价格组成条款，双方签字等内容的页面应当上传。&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">进口合同有电子文本的，</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">可上传合同的PDF格式文件，同时上传纸质合同的第一页和所有签章页。&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">进口合同为外文的，</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">应将以下条款翻译成中文，并将翻译文本签章扫描上传：</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><br></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（三）进口货物相关技术资料和说明文件中，属于判定该货物能否享受优惠政策的内容应当上传。&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"padding-top: 4px; padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 4px; max-width: 100%; border-top-width: 2px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; display: inline-block; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin-top: -8px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; float: left; width: 60px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: table; width: 60px; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%; display: table-cell; line-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%; font-style: italic; font-size: 42px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4</em></section></section></section><section style=\"max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 45, 96); float: left; border-color: rgb(0, 45, 96); word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">单证保管的要求</span></strong></section></section></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">减免税无纸申报后，要注意其纸质单证的保管哦！</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br></p></div>', null, '2017-12-27 19:32:18', '2017-12-28 14:03:25');
INSERT INTO `lessons` VALUES ('30', '想弄懂全国通关一体化来这里', '快来看看', '2', '0', '0', '1', '1', '3', '20', '3', 'http://edu.elinkport.com/storage/uploads/images/nav_18-5a43864a5941d.png', '0.01', '比特币、区块链的技术原理--系统了解比特币及其实操注意事项--掌握虚拟货币全球政策和市场情况--区块链对经济金融、银行、投资领域 1-5 年后的影响--区块链的最新进展和应用趋势', '3', '<ul style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; list-style-position: inside; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-size-adjust: auto;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">比特币爱好者、数字货币从业者</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">新技术爱好者、技术从业人士</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">对未来有规划的程序员</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">找方向的创业者和投资人</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">保险、证券等相关行业从业人员</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">渴望把握未来先机，做出正确选择的人</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">有追求的经济、金融领域从业者</li><li style=\"margin-left: 1.3em; list-style: none;\">对世界好奇，对趋势敏感的人</li></ul>', '<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">8、企业如何与税管中心沟通联系？&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">企业可以通过H2010系统的海关公共服务查询模块、12360微信公众号等渠道查询报关单通关状态，或者致电12360进一步沟通咨询；税收征管中心在与企业进行联系，或要求企业配合中心开展验估作业的时候，一般通过“挂起”报关单通知企业，并预留联系方式，企业可以通过被“挂起”报关单下预留的联系方式联系税管中心。&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important;\">具体流程如下：</span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.通过电子口岸如实、规范录入报关单涉税要素及各项目数据；&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.利用预录人系统的海关计税（费）服务工具计算应缴纳的相关税费；&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3.对系统显示的税费计算结果进行确认，连同报关单预录入内容一并提交海关（进出口企业、单位需在当日对税费进行确认，不予确认的，可重新申报）；&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4.收到海关通关系统发送的回执后，自行办理相关税费缴纳手续。&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: auto; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">已在海关办理汇总征税总担保备案的进出口企业、单位可在申报时选择“汇总征税”模式。</span></p>', null, '2017-12-27 19:40:51', '2018-01-05 15:55:06');
